#### Bountiful Sapling
*Wondrous item, common*
<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

*The wood from this staff is tropical in origin and appears far from dead. Vines and leaves still cling to it and it gives off a fresh sweet smell.*
<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

Planting the bottom of this staff in fresh soil for 8 hours causes it to grow one fruit of your choice. This fruit provides enough nourishment for the day and heals 1d4 hit points. An hour after it is picked, the fruit rots and loses its potency.

